11. Bh6+ { The first move of a forced checkmate. } 11... Kg8 12. Ne8
{ Know your checkmate patterns! A Knight on  f6  will end the game with checkmate. Black can't prevent it. }
12... f5 13. Nf6# { A good example of Suffocation mate. } *

