1. e4 c5 { Sicilian Defense } 2. Nf3 e6 { French Variation } 3. Nc3 d5
{ Trying to take control over the center. But that's not a good idea in this particular line! }
4. exd5 { Trading a pair of center pawns. } 4... exd5 5. Bb5+ Bd7
{ 5...Nc6  would have been better @@StartBracket@@+1.0@@EndBracket@@. } 6. Qe2+
