{ Attacking the Queen while defending the Rook.   10...exd5  fails to  11.Ndxb5  axb5  , followed by  12.Bxb5+  or  12.Qxa8  @@StartBracket@@+4.5@@EndBracket@@. }
11. Qg3
{ The only move for White to keep an edge.   11.exd6  is bad because of  11...Bxd6  @@StartBracket@@+0.0@@EndBracket@@. }
