Nxe6 { Another brilliant piece sacrifice. } 16... fxe6 17. Nxb5
{ White now regained three pawns in exchange for two of his minor pieces. But the point is that Black's King is very vulnerable in the middle of the board. }
17... Qe7 18. Nd6+ { White's only move to win the game. } 18... Kf8
{ 18...Qxd6  would have been best @@StartBracket@@+7.0@@EndBracket@@. } 19.
Rhf1+ { Black will lost his Queen next move. It's game over! } *

