{ It is too early to play  7...Ng4  , e.g. in view of  8.Bg5  Bxd4?  9.Bb5+  with check! Black could have castled first, in order to avoid the check. }
8. O-O Ng4
{ By far the best move, and the move with an excellent winrate. White will lose his important dark-squared Bishop. After that, White will have a hard time to deal with Black's dark-squared Bishop @@StartBracket@@-0.5@@EndBracket@@! }
