8. Bf4 { Defending the pawn on  e5  with a second piece. } 8... Nh6
{ Black tries to attack the pawn on  e5  with a third piece next move.   Black's best continuation is  8...f6  , followed by  9.exf6  Nxf6  10.O-O-O  @@StartBracket@@+1.5@@EndBracket@@. }
9. h3 { Preventing Ng4. } 9... O-O 10. O-O-O
