{ Attacking the Knight on  f3  . } 3. Ng5 { Attacking Black's center pawn. }
3... Qd5 { Defending the pawn while attacking the Knight. Not the best move. }
4. d3 { Defending the Knight while inviting Black to capture on  d3  . } 4...
exd3 { Trading pawns. } 5. Bxd3
{ Leaving the  g2  pawn unprotected... On purpose!   5.Nc3  is a better move objectively. }
