{ Grabbing an important center pawn while threatening checkmate on  f2  . } 8.
Nxe4 { Trading pieces, White's best try. } 8... Qxe4+
{ Black is controlling the game @@StartBracket@@-2.0@@EndBracket@@. White will have a hard time to bring his King to safety. }
