{ Challenging White's center pawn. } 4. Bc4 { Attacking the Knight. } 4... Nb6
{ Retreating the Knight while attacking the Bishop. } 5. Bxf7+
{ An unsound sacrifice... } 5... Kxf7 6. Ng5+ Kg8
