9. g3 { The best move for White. It's not game over yet. } 9... Qe4+
{ Forking King and Rook on  h1  . } 10. Qe2 { Activating the Queen. } 10...
Qxh1 11. Nf3 { Saving the Knight. Black's Queen is trapped for now. } 11... Nc6
{ Material is equal, but White's pawns are scattered all over the board @@StartBracket@@-1.5@@EndBracket@@.   11...Nxc4  is possible, but this actually helps White, since that pawn is currently blocking White's own pieces @@StartBracket@@-0.5@@EndBracket@@. }
