{ Developing a Knight with tempo. Black now has to move his Queen for the second time in only 4 moves. When you start playing chess, try to avoid to bring your Queen out in the first few moves. Especially avoid bringing your Queen to  d4  ,  d5  ,  e4  or  e5  , where she can be chased away by one of White's Knights with tempo @@StartBracket@@+2.0@@EndBracket@@. }
