{ Capturing a pawn, threatening to capture the Queen next move with a discovered check from the Bishop. }
10. Rxf2 { A necessary intervention... } 10... Qxf2+
{ 10...Bxf2+  is equally good. But by taking with the Queen, there is a chance that Black will finish the game very soon! }
